thread.title: Mr T J C Alexander-Head
thread.title_full: Ace Rental Cars Australia & New Zealand reviewed by Mr T J C Alexander-Head

author: Mr T J C Alexander-Head
title: Mr T J C Alexander-Head
text: Pick up was a pleasure. Vehicle fully explained to us, car seemd in showroom condition. It was well maintained and gave no problems. Return was easy with an immediate offer to run us back into town.
